headline: GE Aerospace Board of Directors Authorizes Regular Quarterly Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of GE Aerospace (NYSE: GE) today declared a $0.36 per share dividend on the outstanding common stock of the Company. The dividend is payable October 27, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on September 29, 2025. The ex-dividend date is September 29, 2025.
